CONTENTS:
---------
Makefile	makefile for an stand-alone executabe of the StHbtMaker
SOURCE_THIS     script to set the correct path for shared libirary libstd++
hbt.cc		main function to run the StHbtMaker as a stand-alone executable

INSTRUCTIONS:
-------------
0.) go to a clean directory
    cd <destination>
1.) cvs co StRoot/StHbtMaker
2.) cvs co StRoot/StarClassLibrary
3.) copy the Make directory to where you want to create the program
    cp StRoot/StHbtMaker/doc/Make <destination>
    cd StRoot/StHbtMaker/doc/Make <destination>
4.) source SOURCE_THIS
5.) edit the Makefile so that the STROOT variable points to the StRoot directory
5.) make hbt
6.) hbt <eventNumber> asc/bin <inputFile>

